metadata.description:
You did it. As the observer, everything in this timeline is based on your viewpoint and your decisions. The moment you chose to measure the problem, the final state was revealed. There were eight supersitional states and state seven was chosen at random to be the final state.

This problem will forever be impacted by your decision, like the blockchain you have made an immutable imprint on the future outcome of this problem. Whether you choose to hold or sell the token will be the next point on its journey.
metadata.name: Final State
